title: National Park visits by month
name: National Park visits by month
description: The map is based on park visits by month and for the entire year of 2006. The data source is  http://www.nps.gov/   The total number of visits to all of the national parks, monuments and historical sites came to nearly 439 million. Month of July had the maximum number of visits recorded (53.4 million) while the month of February had just over 24.2 million. Washington Monument had maximum number of visits for all 12 months, and the months of both the highest and the lowest number of visits are March and February respectively.
